  body
    header.main-header
      .main-header__container
        a(href='/')
          img.logo__img(src='/public/img/res/Logo.png' alt)
    main#main
      section#login-section.login-section
        h3.login-section__title
          | Registrarse

          .underline
            span
            img(src='/public/img/res/pata.png' alt)
            span
        .login-section__container
          .login-section__header
          .logo-user
            img(src='/public/img/login/user.png' alt)
          img.login-section__logo(src='/public/img/res/Logo.png' alt)
          p.
            
            Para la compra de artículos en nuestra tienda debe estar registrado. Usaremos los datos introducidos aquí para ponernos en contacto con usted.
          form#register-form.login-section__form.login-section__form--register(action="/users/register" method="POST")
            .form-container
              label.form-container__img(for='name')
                img(src='/public/img/login/datos.png' alt)
              |
              |
              input#name(autofocus type='text' name='name' required)
              label.placeholder.move-placeholder(for='name') Nombre(s)
            .form-container
              label.form-container__img(for='lastname')
                img(src='/public/img/login/datos.png' alt)
              |
              |
              input#lastname(type='text' name='lastname' required)
              label.placeholder(for='lastname') Apellido(s)
            .form-container
              label.form-container__img(for='phone')
                img(src='/public/img/login/phone.png' alt)
              |
              |
              input#phone(type='tel' name='phone' maxlength='8' required)
              label.placeholder(for='phone') Número de Teléfono
            .form-container
              label.form-container__img(for='email')
                img(src='/public/img/login/email.png' alt)
              |
              |
              input#email.email(type='email' name='email' required)
              label.placeholder(for='email') Correo Electrónico
            .form-container
              label.form-container__img(for='address')
                img(src='/public/img/login/address.png' alt)
              |
              |
              input#address(type='text' name='address' required)
              label.placeholder(for='address') Dirección
            .form-container
              label.form-container__img(for='username')
                img(src='/public/img/login/user-input.png' alt)
              |
              |
              input#username(type='text' name='username' required)
              label.placeholder(for='username') Nombre de Usuario
            .form-container
              label.form-container__img(for='password')
                img(src='/public/img/login/password.png' alt)
              |
              |
              input#password.password(type='password' name='password' required)
              label.placeholder(for='password') Contraseña
              span#show-password.show-password
                img(src='/public/img/login/show-eye.png' alt)
            .form-container
              label.form-container__img(for='confirm_password')
                img(src='/public/img/login/password.png' alt)
              |
              |
              input#confirm-password.password(type='password' name='password2' required)
              label.placeholder(for='confirm-password') Confirmar Contraseña
              span#confirm-show-password.show-password
                img(src='/public/img/login/show-eye.png' alt)
            label(for='checkbox')
              input#checkbox.checkbox-input(type='checkbox' name='notify')
              span.my-checkbox
              |
              |
              span.msg-checkbox Notificarme productos nuevos
            div
              input.btn#btn-register(type='submit' value='Registrarse')
              |
              |
              a.btn.btn-cancel(href='/' type='submit').

                Cancelar

          span.line-login
            | ¿Ya tienes una cuenta? 

            a(href='/users/login') Accede Aquí
        #back-email-send.send-email
          .send-email__header Recuperar Contraseña
          .send-email__title
            img(src='/public/img/login/confirm-email.png' alt)
